text: Þis wæs gedon ymbeVIIIIhund wintra & seofan & syxtig on þy eahteoþan geare þæs þe Oswald bisceop to folgoþe feng.
Sancta Maria & Sanctus Michahel cum Sancto Petro& eallum Godes halgum gemiltsien þis healdendum.
Gif hwa buton gewyrhtum hit abrecan wille hæbbe him wið God gemæne buton he to dædbote gecyrre.
